{"tid":843183,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"點解今日放假? 因為今日係國際音樂日","createTime":"2018-10-01T03:14:26.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-01T07:47:26.000Z","uid":123613,"like":10,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"a70db10486cec07b5dbff3dcc3120fdbf1febc20","tid":843183,"uid":123613,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-01T03:14:26.000Z","msg":"國際音樂理事會（International Music Council，縮寫為IMC）成立於1949年，是聯合國教科文組織在音樂方面的諮詢機構。其宗旨是促進世界音樂文化、音樂教育與音樂研究的交流。總部設在巴黎聯合國教科文之家，下設國際音樂家協會、國際音樂教育協會、國際現代音樂協會等機構，現有會員國六十多個，國際組織委員會十八個，個人會員及名譽會員若干。<br />\n<br />\n國際音樂理事會每兩年開大會一次。1980年召開第十八屆大會，統一<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">每年10月1日為國際音樂日。</span></strong>"},{"pid":"ba31c8eb52aeaa6b0c5017f2ff78a1aa6a028e9d","tid":843183,"uid":123613,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-01T03:48:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f12ea3e44233d13a39ec1718e919fb41eb43234c","tid":843183,"uid":53026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-01T03:51:16.000Z","msg":"又係49年成立<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dc4c1bb1bef443fb80b8255da745817a24bf8f2c","tid":843183,"uid":191762,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-01T03:54:21.000Z","msg":"昆士蘭省今日英女王生日"},{"pid":"d861b4d4dfd9a7d6bc1e51b6eeacb110a1623bf0","tid":843183,"uid":123613,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-01T07:47:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}